attribute=20
  listed here. Applications can use the ODMQueryCapability function to =
determine=20
  if a DMS supports a given document attribute.=20
  <P>Note that the ODMA standard does not currently define maximum =
lengths for=20
  any specific document attribute. This is DMS specific. In most cases =
the DMS=20
  will truncate the attribute value returned if it does not fit in the =
caller=20
  supplied buffer.=20
